data.description: Welcome to this charming and meticulously updated 2-bedroom, 1-bath Ranch style home nestled in the heart of the desirable town of Mt. Ephraim. Boasting a prime location with convenient access to all major bridges, highways, Philadelphia, and the beautiful shore points, this residence offers both comfort and convenience.  Step inside to discover a thoughtfully updated kitchen, perfect for whipping up delicious meals and entertaining guests. The modern bathroom adds a touch of luxury, while the vinyl floors throughout provide both durability and easy maintenance.  There is also a newer HVAC and hot water heater as well!    Outside, the property is enhanced by a brand new white vinyl fence that not only adds curb appeal but also ensures privacy. The extra-wide driveway offers ample parking space for you and your guests, while a newly built shed in the rear provides additional storage for all your tools and outdoor equipment.  Whether you're a first-time homebuyer looking to start a new chapter or someone looking to downsize without compromising on style and comfort, this property is brimming with potential and is ready to welcome you home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your own slice of paradise in Mt. Ephraim.
